♪ <i>She has to discipline her body </i>♪

1605
01:54:48,291 --> 01:54:53,166
♪ <i>'Cause she knows that it's demandin' </i>♪

1606
01:54:53,875 --> 01:54:59,375
♪ <i>To defeat those evil machines </i>♪

1607
01:55:02,416 --> 01:55:05,750
♪ <i>I know she can beat them </i>♪

1608
